    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Brevem pro futuris temporibus securitate et firmitatem ad
                        memoriam retinendam, qualiter vel quibus presencia bonorum hominum, corum
                        nomina subter leguntur, investivit <persName key="#Papal_court_officer"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Papal_court_officer"><name ref="Pasquale"
                            >Pascalis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> sancte Romane ecclesie et <persName
                            ref="#people/376" key="#Bishops">Gerardus</persName> episcopus sancte
                        Laudensis ecclesie, nec non et <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Missus_regis"><name ref="Dido"
                                >Dido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs>
                        <rs key="#Missus_regis">missi</rs> domni <persName ref="#people/80"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Karlomanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">regis</rs> per colunna de casa et <rs
                            key="#Other_minor_officer">servo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_minor_officer"><name ref="Garipertus"
                            >Gariberto</name></persName>, <persName key="#Other_minor_officer"><name
                                ref="Adalbertus">Adelberto</name></persName> servo monasterii in
                        honore <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53"
                            key="#Other_minor_officer #Monasteries">sancte Resurectionis atque
                            sanctorum martirum Systi et Fabiani</orgName>, quod domna <persName
                            ref="#people/55" key="#Queen">Angilberga</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatrix</rs> a fundamentis <placeName ref="#places/43"
                            >Placentie</placeName> construxit, per iussionem dompni Karlomanni regis
                        de <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/90"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/612"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                >Faeto</placeName></geogName> atque curte <geogName
                            ref="#estates/91"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/618"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                >Muciaria</placeName></geogName> seu et de <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massariciis</rs> in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/293"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/608"
                                key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >Vualdo Meleto</placeName></geogName> cum ipso Vualdo cum omnibus
                        abiacenciis et pertinenciis, cum <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et
                            ancillis</rs> ad ipsas prenominatas duas curtes aspicientibus in
                        integrum ad partem predicti monasterii ad proprietatem habendam iuxta ipsum
                        preceptum quas domnus Karlomannus rex a presenti die pro remedium anime sue
                        prefato monasterio contulit <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >proprietario iure</rs> omni tempore habendum atque possidendum. Factum
                        est hanc investitura in ipsa curte Faedo, anno dompni Karlomanni regis in
                        Italia II, mense augusto, indictione XII. + Ego Iohannes episcopus <rs
                            key="#Papal_court_officer">legatus</rs> sancte sedis apostolice sicut
                        supra peregi et subscripsi. + Pascalis episcopus legatus sancte sedis
                        apostolice sicut supra peregi et subscripsi. + Gerardus episcopus qui
                        iussione regia egi subscripsi. + Ego Dido qui iussione regia egi subscripsi.
                        Ego <persName><name ref="Gausus">Gauso</name></persName> ibi fui.
                                <persName><name ref="Riprandus">Ripran</name></persName> interfui. +
                                <persName><name ref="Ilderadus">Ilderado</name></persName> interfui
                        + Ego <persName><name ref="Teobaldus">Tethaldo</name></persName> interfui.
                                <persName><name ref="Redaldus">Redaldo</name></persName> ibi fui.
                            <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Sigebrandus"
                            >Sigiprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">scavino</rs> ibi fui. Zuzeprando ibi fui. + Ego Gariprando
                        ibi fui. Ego Riebertus ibi fui. + Ego Appo ibi fui. + Pedebertus ibi fui. +
                        Esenbertus ibi fui. + Ego Stadebertus ibi fui. Signum manus + Ermernulfi
                        comes interfui. Signum manus + Gauselmi filius Berte qui interfuit. Signum
                        manus + Boniperti de Pravello qui interfuit. Signum manus + Cristofali de
                        Silvani qui interfuit. Signum manus + Nanteri ex genere Francorum qui
                        interfuit. Signum manus + Ansemondi ex genere Francorum qui interfuit.
                        Signum manus + Ingelberti ex genere Francorum qui interfuit. Signum manus +
                        Guilleranni vicecomiti qui interfuit. Signum manus + Teomulti de Isella ex
                        genere Francorum qui interfuit. + Ego Vuido notarius hunc breve scripsi et
                        interfui. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
